Get libraries for matching with specific mode and type

get_libs.Rd

Get libraries for matching with specific mode and type

get_libs(mode = c("Pos", "Neg"), acq = c("dda", "aif"))

Arguments

mode

Acquisition mode. Default is 'Pos'
acq

Acquisition type, either dda or aif. Default is 'dda'

Value

A tibble containing all libraries for the chosen mode and type.

Examples

get_libs(mode = 'Pos', acq = 'dda')
